---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions"
  description="Terms and Conditions of Sonia Buddy for website and mobile app users, bus timetable information, vehicle rental listings and third-party services."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p>Effective Date: April 19, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> April 19, 2026</p>
        <p>
          These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the Sonia Buddy mobile application
          and related website, collectively called the "Service". By downloading, installing, accessing, or using
          Sonia Buddy, you agree to be legally bound by these Terms. If you do not agree with these Terms, you must
          discontinue use of the Service immediately.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is a travel information and listing platform for West Bengal. Our Service helps users search
          bus timetable information, route details, direct and indirect travel options, and driver-included vehicle
          rental listings such as car rental, bus rental, toto rent, pickup van, ambulance, wedding bus, tour car,
          and school bus services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
          You must be at least 18 years of age to register for or use Sonia Buddy services that involve account
          creation, booking requests, owner listing submission, or direct communication with service providers.
        </p>
        <p>
          By using the Service, you represent and warrant that you meet this age requirement and have the legal
          capacity to enter into a binding agreement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>2. User Accounts</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information, including your name, email address,
          phone number, and address where required for account creation, listing submission, booking requests,
          support, or communication.
        </p>
        <p>
          You are solely responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all
          activities that occur under your account.
        </p>
        <p>
          You agree to notify Sonia Buddy immediately of any unauthorized access to or use of your account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>3. Bus Timetable and Route Information</h2>
        <p>
          Bus timings, routes, stops, middle-stop suggestions, direct routes, indirect routes, and location
          information provided for West Bengal are estimates compiled from publicly available, user-submitted,
          and operator-provided data.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy tries to provide useful and updated information, but we do not guarantee the accuracy,
          completeness, availability, or real-time precision of any bus schedule, route, stop, fare, travel time,
          or operator information.
        </p>
        <p>
          Bus schedules may change due to traffic, weather, road conditions, operator decisions, festivals,
          holidays, strikes, breakdowns, or other local reasons. Users are strongly advised to arrive at the bus
          stop 10–15 minutes before the scheduled time and verify important travel details locally when needed.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is not liable for delays, missed buses, lost time, missed appointments, financial loss,
          or any direct or indirect loss caused by reliance on bus timetable or route information.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>4. Vehicle Rental Listings</h2>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy provides a platform where vehicle owners, drivers, agencies, and service providers may list
          driver-included rental services such as cars, buses, toto, auto, pickup van, ambulance, wedding vehicles,
          tour vehicles, school-office vehicles, and goods transport vehicles.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is not a transport company, travel agency, taxi operator, ambulance operator, or vehicle owner.
          We do not directly provide rental vehicles, drivers, ambulance services, tours, or transport services.
        </p>
        <p>
          All rental discussions, price confirmation, availability, pickup point, route, safety checks, payment,
          cancellation, refund, and service quality are handled directly between the user and the respective owner,
          driver, agency, or service provider.
        </p>
        <p>
          Users should verify vehicle condition, driver identity, documents, permit, insurance, pricing, service
          terms, and safety before confirming any rental or travel arrangement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>5. Third-Party Services and Tour Bookings</h2>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy operates as a platform that connects users with independent local travel agencies, vehicle
          owners, drivers, ambulance providers, goods transport providers, and tour operators.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are not responsible for the quality, safety, legality, availability, pricing, refund, cancellation,
          behavior, delay, or delivery of services provided by any third-party service provider.
        </p>
        <p>
          All financial transactions, refunds, cancellations, and disputes relating to tours, rentals, bookings,
          or transport services must be resolved directly between the user and the respective agency, owner,
          driver, or service provider.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>6. Ambulance and Emergency Services Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy may display ambulance rental or emergency vehicle listings submitted by owners or service
          providers. Sonia Buddy does not operate ambulance services and does not guarantee emergency response,
          medical assistance, ambulance arrival time, driver availability, or hospital coordination.
        </p>
        <p>
          In a medical emergency, users should contact official emergency numbers, nearby hospitals, local ambulance
          services, or local authorities directly. Sonia Buddy should not be treated as an emergency medical service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>7. Owner and Listing Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>
          Vehicle owners, drivers, agencies, and service providers who submit listings are responsible for providing
          accurate and lawful information, including vehicle type, photos, service city, contact number, WhatsApp
          number, price text, seats/capacity, availability, and description.
        </p>
        <p>
          Owners must not upload false, misleading, copied, abusive, illegal, or unauthorized photos or information.
          Sonia Buddy may review, edit, reject, hide, suspend, or remove any listing if it appears fake, unsafe,
          misleading, outdated, duplicate, spammy, or harmful to users.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>8. User Responsibility Before Booking</h2>
        <p>
          Before confirming any rental, booking, tour, transport, or travel plan, users should directly confirm all
          important details with the owner, driver, agency, or operator.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Confirm final price, extra charges, waiting charges, tolls, parking, fuel, night charges, and cancellation rules.</li>
          <li>Confirm vehicle condition, driver details, pickup time, pickup location, route, and service availability.</li>
          <li>Confirm whether the service provider has necessary documents, permits, insurance, and local authorization.</li>
          <li>Use personal judgment and safety precautions before sharing money, documents, or personal details.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>9. Prohibited Use</h2>
        <p>When using Sonia Buddy, you agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the Service for any unlawful, fraudulent, abusive, harmful, or misleading purpose.</li>
          <li>Submit false, misleading, spam, duplicate, malicious, or unauthorized route, stop, schedule, listing, or booking information.</li>
          <li>Attempt to hack, reverse engineer, decompile, disassemble, scrape, copy, or tamper with the app, website, database, or infrastructure.</li>
          <li>Use bots, scrapers, automated tools, or bulk extraction methods to access or copy any part of the Service without written permission.</li>
          <li>Upload illegal, offensive, copyrighted, fake, or misleading photos or content.</li>
          <li>Misuse another person's contact number, identity, business name, vehicle details, or listing information.</li>
          <li>Harass, threaten, abuse, cheat, or mislead other users, owners, drivers, agencies, or Sonia Buddy staff.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>10. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content within the Service, including the Sonia Buddy name, logo, design, layout, route database,
          search features, UI elements, graphics, text, and software, is the property of Sonia Buddy or its
          respective content providers and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.
        </p>
        <p>
          No part of the Service may be copied, reproduced, distributed, scraped, modified, published, sold,
          or used commercially without prior written consent from Sonia Buddy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>11. Data Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Your use of the Service is also governed by our Privacy Policy, which explains how we collect, use,
          store, share, and protect your personal information. By using Sonia Buddy, you consent to the practices
          described in our Privacy Policy.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can read our Privacy Policy here: <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>12. No Guarantee of Continuous Service</h2>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy may update, modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of the Service at any time, including
          bus route pages, listing features, search tools, owner dashboard, reports, analytics, or rental listing
          functions.
        </p>
        <p>
          We do not guarantee that the Service will always be available, error-free, secure, uninterrupted, or
          compatible with every device, browser, or network.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>13. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, Sonia Buddy shall not be liable for any direct, indirect,
          incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to your use of the
          website, mobile app, bus timetable information, rental listings, third-party services, or communication
          with owners, drivers, agencies, or operators.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is not liable for delays, accidents, cancellations, service failures, wrong information,
          payment disputes, refund disputes, owner behavior, driver behavior, vehicle condition, medical emergency
          outcomes, or any loss caused by third-party service providers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>14. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Sonia Buddy, its owners, team members, partners, service
          providers, and affiliates from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, costs, or expenses arising from
          your use of the Service, your violation of these Terms, your submitted content, your listing information,
          or your interaction with any third-party service provider.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>15. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our website or app may contain links to third-party websites, phone numbers, WhatsApp links, maps,
          service provider pages, payment pages, or external resources. Sonia Buddy is not responsible for the
          content, policies, safety, accuracy, or practices of those third-party services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>16. Modifications to the Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Updated Terms will be posted on this page with
          a revised effective date. Your continued use of the Service after any changes means you accept the
          revised Terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>17. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. Any disputes arising
          out of or relating to these Terms or the Service shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the
          competent courts of West Bengal, India.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>18. Severability</h2>
        <p>
          If any provision of these Terms is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions shall
          continue in full force and effect.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>19. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions, concerns, complaints, listing removal requests, or support requests regarding these
          Terms, please contact us:
        </p>
        <p><strong>Support Email:</strong> zisakhoofficial@gmail.com</p>
        <p>Or visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>